=== suppression_master - sentinel focus ===

--- Items required for procedure ---
Microsoft Sentinel
Ticketing system

--- Procedure ---
1. Visit Microsoft Sentinel
2. Choose relevant workspace
3. Automation in left hand menu
4. Create "Automation Rule"
5. Give the automation rule a name, similar to ones already present <alert name/purpose of automation rule>
6. Input Trigger "When incident is created"
7. Input Conditions
8. If incident provider equals All AND Analytic rule name contains "Ti Map" AND IPAddress <equals bad indicator IP>
9. Scrolll down to Actions and change to closed as <TP or FP> and input comment "Handed to client for follow up" or "<whatever>"
10. Set Rule expiration can be in 3 months or never > Status "Disabled/Enabled"
